.com/u/Fargo2333", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1537154508, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8ebc/8773/350024_mini.png?m=1566891066", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8ebc/8773/350024_mini.png?m=1566891066", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 350024}, "last_reply_by": "Daming", "last_touched": 1618894658, "title": "提了离职要走吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/771707", "created": 1618822492, "content": "上周拿到了 offer，提了离职，薪资涨幅大概 35%左右，但是工作时间变成了大小周，9-6，现单位是 955 。今天领导也找我聊了聊，劝我留下来，给调了职级，薪资加了 1k 。有点纠结，不知道该走还是留，各位 V 友有啥想法吗？", "content_rendered": "<p>上周拿到了 offer，提了离职，薪资涨幅大概 35%左右，但是工作时间变成了大小周，9-6，现单位是 955 。今天领导也找我聊了聊，劝我留下来，给调了职级，薪资加了 1k 。有点纠结，不知道该走还是留，各位 V 友有啥想法吗？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1618822492, "replies": 64, "id": 771707}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1617610541", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1617610541", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 11304, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1617610541", "stars": 2006, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": "work"}, "member": {"username": "yiiouo", "website": "", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a343/bf09/278190_mini.png?m=1591066925", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/yiiouo", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1514790248, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a343/bf09/278190_mini.png?m=1591066925", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a343/bf09/278190_mini.png?m=1591066925", "location": "佛山", "btc": "", "id": 278190}, "last_reply_by": "idragonet", "last_touched": 1618823065, "title": "收到 offer，要不要跳槽？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/771628", "created": 1618809436, "content": "人在佛山，现在年收入 15 左右，大小周，不加班，上班 20 多分钟就到了，公司氛围还行。\n\n上周有朋友内推我到碧桂园，已经发 offer 了，年收入 18+，双休，加班严重，8 个前端走剩 3 个了，后端也又了不少人，上班时间要 40 多分钟。\n\n刚提了离职，部门技术老大劝我留下，说这里机会更多，可以让你负责不同项目。因为部门在上一年才建立不久，所以前端基本上都是我负责管理和开发。\n\n现在很纠结要不要过去碧桂园，因为自己的学历只有大专，能去到佛山这边的大公司，简历也会好看点，但现在公司的老大也确实给机会我，让我负责前端这块。各位大佬给下意见…", "content_rendered": "<p>人在佛山，现在年收入 15 左右，大小周，不加班，上班 20 多分钟就到了，公司氛围还行。</p>\n<p>上周有朋友内推我到碧桂园，已经发 offer 了，年收入 18+，双休，加班严重，8 个前端走剩 3 个了，后端也又了不少人，上班时间要 40 多分钟。</p>\n<p>刚提了离职，部门技术老大劝我留下，说这里机会更多，可以让你负责不同项目。因为部门在上一年才建立不久，所以前端基本上都是我负责管理和开发。</p>\n<p>现在很纠结要不要过去碧桂园，因为自己的学历只有大专，能去到佛山这边的大公司，简历也会好看点，但现在公司的老大也确实给机会我，让我负责前端这块。各位大佬给下意见…</p>\n", "last_modified": 1618809436, "replies": 60, "id": 771628}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1615111825", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1615111825", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 14553, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1615111825", "stars": 1781, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"username": "YoungKing6", "website": "", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/87ed/7214/495591_mini.png?m=1607773757", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/YoungKing6", "tagline": "More than", "twitter": "", "created": 1592622490, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/87ed/7214/495591_mini.png?m=1607773757", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/87ed/7214/495591_mini.png?m=1607773757", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 495591}, "last_reply_by": "goodryb", "last_touched": 1618895152, "title": "真想回到用 iMessage 聊天的时代 微信和 QQ 真的过于冗杂", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/771830", "created": 1618885309, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last